messages.messageBody:
I'm so GEEKED that this is being held in N. Carolina and that is only
a little over 8 hours from Pcola....I AM SOOOOO THERE!!! WOOT!

:-) BTW...the link for the YMCA doesn't work on the Live and Learn
Site but I googled it....wow, totally beautiful.

I cannot hardly stand that we have a year but that is alright.
Sticking to this site and reading positive articles about unschooling
is helping me to stay focused although, I've had a couple of ugly
thoughts creep into my mind but thanks to some wise advice, I'm
speaking positively in order to rid them.

~Sandy
